{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":871,"text":"There are about 5,000 women here today."},{"time":8501,"text":"Among us, 1,250 have been\nor will be sexually assaulted"},{"time":14678,"text":"at some point in our lives."},{"time":19518,"text":"One in four."},{"time":24050,"text":"Only 10 percent will report it."},{"time":28998,"text":"The other 90 percent\ntake refuge in silence --"},{"time":35332,"text":"half of them, because the incident\ninvolves a close family member"},{"time":40738,"text":"or someone they know,"},{"time":43173,"text":"and that makes it much more difficult\nto deal with and talk about."},{"time":49625,"text":"The other half don't talk about it"},{"time":53485,"text":"because they fear they wonâ€™t be believed."},{"time":57450,"text":"And they're right -- because we don't."}]},{"cues":[{"time":63054,"text":"Today I want to share with you\nwhy I think we don't believe them."},{"time":68738,"text":"We don't believe them because when\na woman tells what happened to her,"},{"time":73023,"text":"she tells us things we can't imagine,"},{"time":76634,"text":"things that disturb us,"},{"time":78077,"text":"things we don't expect to hear,"},{"time":80349,"text":"things that shock us."},{"time":83009,"text":"We expect to hear stories like this one:"},{"time":89467,"text":"\"Girl raped near\nthe Mitre Railroad tracks."},{"time":92593,"text":"It happened at midnight\nas she was on her way home."},{"time":96147,"text":"She said that someone\nattacked her from behind,"},{"time":100367,"text":"told her not to scream, said he had a gun\nand that she shouldn't move."},{"time":104687,"text":"He raped her and then fled the scene.\""},{"time":110034,"text":"When we hear or read a story like this,"},{"time":113932,"text":"we immediately visualize it:"},{"time":118212,"text":"the rapist, a depraved lower-class man."},{"time":123162,"text":"And the victim, a young, attractive woman."},{"time":129916,"text":"The image only lasts 10 or 20 seconds,\nand it's dark and two-dimensional;"},{"time":135723,"text":"there's no movement, no sound;\nit's as if there were no people involved."},{"time":141713,"text":"But when a woman tells her story,\nit doesn't fit in 10 or 20 seconds."}]},{"cues":[{"time":148542,"text":"The following is the testimony\nof a woman I'll call \"Ana.\""},{"time":154272,"text":"She's one of the 85 women I interviewed"},{"time":157609,"text":"while conducting research\non sexual assault."},{"time":164115,"text":"Ana told me:"},{"time":169191,"text":"\"I had gone with the girls in the office\nto the same pub we always go to."},{"time":174482,"text":"We met some guys,"},{"time":176015,"text":"and I hooked up with this super\ncool guy; we talked a lot."},{"time":181911,"text":"Around 4am, I told my friends\nit was time to go."},{"time":184928,"text":"They wanted to stay."},{"time":186727,"text":"So, the guy asked me where I lived"},{"time":189650,"text":"and said if it was OK with me,\nhe'd drive me home."},{"time":192501,"text":"I agreed, and we left."}]},{"cues":[{"time":195564,"text":"At a stoplight, he told me\nhe liked me and touched my leg."},{"time":200660,"text":"I don't like a guy\nto approach me that way,"},{"time":203344,"text":"but he had been affectionate all night."},{"time":206373,"text":"I thought, 'I shouldn't be so paranoid."},{"time":209238,"text":"What if I say something but he\ndidn't mean anything by it,"},{"time":212022,"text":"and I offend him?'"},{"time":214491,"text":"When he should have made a turn,\nhe kept going straight."},{"time":217317,"text":"I thought he had made\na mistake, and I said,"},{"time":219704,"text":"'You should have turned there.'"},{"time":222260,"text":"But something felt off."},{"time":225202,"text":"Thinking back, I wonder,"},{"time":226745,"text":"'Why didn't I pay attention\nto what I was feeling?'"}]},{"cues":[{"time":231487,"text":"When he pulled over near the highway,"},{"time":234616,"text":"that's when I got scared."},{"time":237769,"text":"But he told me to relax, that he liked me,"},{"time":240433,"text":"and that nothing would happen\nunless I wanted it to."},{"time":243015,"text":"He was nice."},{"time":245296,"text":"I didn't say anything,"},{"time":246484,"text":"because I was afraid he would get angry,"},{"time":248580,"text":"and that things would get worse."},{"time":251008,"text":"I thought he might have a gun\nin the glove compartment."},{"time":254819,"text":"Suddenly, he jumped on me\nand tried to kiss me."},{"time":258722,"text":"I said no. I wanted to push him away,\nbut he was holding my arms down."},{"time":263658,"text":"When I wriggled free, I tried to open\nthe door, but it was locked."},{"time":268289,"text":"And even if I had gotten out,\nwhere would I have gone?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":274028,"text":"I told him he wasn't the kind of guy\nwho needed to do that to be with a girl,"},{"time":279226,"text":"and that I liked him, too,\nbut not in that way."},{"time":282241,"text":"I tried to calm him down."},{"time":284901,"text":"I said nice things about him."},{"time":287317,"text":"I talked to him as if\nI were his older sister."},{"time":291344,"text":"Suddenly, he covered\nmy mouth with one hand"},{"time":295004,"text":"and with the other hand\nhe unbuckled his belt."},{"time":299043,"text":"I thought right then he would kill me,\nstrangle me, you know?"},{"time":305551,"text":"I never felt so alone,"},{"time":308096,"text":"like I had been kidnapped."},{"time":310550,"text":"I asked him to finish quickly\nand then take me home.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":315651,"text":"How did you feel listening to this story?"},{"time":319765,"text":"Surely, several questions arose."},{"time":325279,"text":"For example: Why didn't she roll down\nthe window and call for help?"},{"time":332420,"text":"Why didn't she get out of the car\nwhen she felt something bad might happen?"},{"time":337361,"text":"How could she ask him to take her home?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":343277,"text":"Now, when we hear this kind\nof story not on the news"},{"time":347471,"text":"or from someone like me,\npresenting it on a stage like this --"},{"time":354396,"text":"when we're hearing it from someone we know"},{"time":358145,"text":"who chose to entrust us\nwith the story of what happened to them,"},{"time":365507,"text":"we'll have to listen."},{"time":368575,"text":"And we'll hear things\nwe won't be able to understand --"},{"time":374229,"text":"or accept."},{"time":376957,"text":"And then doubts, questions\nand suspicion will creep in."},{"time":384253,"text":"And that is going to make us feel\nreally bad and guilty."}]},{"cues":[{"time":390122,"text":"So to protect ourselves\nfrom the discomfort, we have an option."},{"time":396400,"text":"We turn up the volume\non all the parts of the story"},{"time":402018,"text":"that we expected to hear:"},{"time":404469,"text":"a gun in the glove compartment,\nthe locked doors, the isolated location."},{"time":411537,"text":"And we turn down the volume\non all the parts of the story"},{"time":415732,"text":"that we didn't expect to hear"},{"time":417894,"text":"and that we don't want to hear;"},{"time":421095,"text":"like when she tells him\nthat she liked him, too,"},{"time":426400,"text":"or when she tells us she spoke to him\nas if she were his older sister,"},{"time":430526,"text":"or that she asked him to take her home."}]},{"cues":[{"time":434939,"text":"Why do we do this?"},{"time":438015,"text":"It's so we can believe her;"},{"time":440755,"text":"so we can feel confident\nthat she really was a victim."},{"time":447797,"text":"I call this \"victimization of the victim.\""},{"time":452112,"text":"\"Victimization,\" because in order\nto believe she's innocent,"},{"time":456918,"text":"that she's a victim,"},{"time":458702,"text":"we need to think of her\nas helpless, paralyzed, mute."},{"time":467268,"text":"But there's another way\nto avoid the discomfort."},{"time":472167,"text":"And it's exactly the opposite:"},{"time":475395,"text":"we turn up the volume on the things\nwe didn't expect to hear,"},{"time":480111,"text":"such as \"I spoke nicely to him,\"\n\"I asked him to take me home,\""},{"time":483743,"text":"\"I asked him to finish quickly,\""},{"time":486683,"text":"and we turn down the volume\non the things we did expect to hear:"},{"time":491008,"text":"the gun in the glove compartment,"},{"time":493209,"text":"the isolation."},{"time":498234,"text":"Why do we do this?"},{"time":500839,"text":"We do it so we can cling to the doubts"},{"time":505606,"text":"and feel more comfortable about them."}]},{"cues":[{"time":508310,"text":"Then, new questions arise, for instance:"},{"time":515836,"text":"Who told her go to those clubs?"},{"time":519452,"text":"You saw how she and her friends\nwere dressed, right?"},{"time":523050,"text":"Those miniskirts, those necklines?"},{"time":526164,"text":"What do you expect?"},{"time":528805,"text":"Questions that aren't really questions,\nbut rather, judgments --"},{"time":534631,"text":"judgments that end in a verdict:"},{"time":539302,"text":"she asked for it."},{"time":543164,"text":"That finding would be verified by the fact"},{"time":546545,"text":"that she didn't mention having\nstruggled to avoid being raped."},{"time":552475,"text":"So that means she didn't resist."},{"time":558102,"text":"It means she consented."},{"time":560641,"text":"If she asked for it and allowed it,"},{"time":564743,"text":"how are we calling it rape?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":568158,"text":"I call this \"blaming the victim.\""},{"time":573476,"text":"These arguments that serve us\nboth to blame and to victimize,"},{"time":580244,"text":"we all have them in our heads, at hand --"},{"time":585777,"text":"including victims and perpetrators."},{"time":589853,"text":"So much so, that when Ana came to me,"},{"time":594592,"text":"she told me she didn't know"},{"time":597827,"text":"if her testimony was going\nto be of any use,"},{"time":601914,"text":"because she wasn't sure\nif what happened to her qualified as rape."},{"time":610294,"text":"Ana believed, like most of us,"},{"time":612978,"text":"that rape is more like armed robbery --"},{"time":617378,"text":"a violent act that lasts 4 or 5 minutes --"},{"time":622254,"text":"and not smooth talking from a nice guy"},{"time":625960,"text":"that lasts all night and ends\nin a kidnapping."},{"time":633800,"text":"When she felt afraid she might be killed,"},{"time":636920,"text":"she was afraid to be left with scars,"},{"time":640467,"text":"and she had to give her body to avoid it."},{"time":644075,"text":"That's when she knew that rape\nwas something different."}]},{"cues":[{"time":650317,"text":"Ana had never talked\nabout this with anyone."},{"time":655427,"text":"She could have turned to her family,"},{"time":658583,"text":"but she didn't."},{"time":660811,"text":"She didn't because she was afraid."},{"time":664097,"text":"She was afraid the person\nshe'd choose to tell her story to"},{"time":670072,"text":"would have the same reaction\nas the rest of us:"},{"time":674210,"text":"they'd have doubts, suspicions;"},{"time":678360,"text":"those same questions we always have\nwhen it comes to things like this."},{"time":683529,"text":"And if that had happened,"},{"time":685477,"text":"it would have been worse, perhaps,\nthan the rape itself."},{"time":690195,"text":"She could have talked\nto a friend or a sister."},{"time":695261,"text":"And with her partner, it would\nhave been extremely difficult:"},{"time":699178,"text":"the slightest hint of doubt\non his face or in his voice"},{"time":703529,"text":"would have been devastating for her"},{"time":706227,"text":"and would have probably meant\nthe end of their relationship."},{"time":711417,"text":"Ana keeps silent\nbecause deep down she knows"},{"time":715561,"text":"that nobody -- none of us,\nnot her family or therapists,"},{"time":721970,"text":"let alone the police or judges --"},{"time":725776,"text":"are willing to hear what Ana\nactually did in that moment."}]},{"cues":[{"time":734784,"text":"First and foremost, Ana said, \"No.\""},{"time":740198,"text":"When she saw that her \"no\" didn't help,"},{"time":743264,"text":"she spoke nicely to him."},{"time":745483,"text":"She tried not to exacerbate his violence"},{"time":748730,"text":"or give him ideas."},{"time":752028,"text":"She talked to him as if everything\nthat was happening were normal,"},{"time":757942,"text":"so he wouldn't be thinking\nthat she would turn him in later."}]},{"cues":[{"time":767779,"text":"Now, I wonder and I ask all of you:"},{"time":773857,"text":"All those things she did --"},{"time":776433,"text":"isn't that considered resisting?"},{"time":780890,"text":"No."},{"time":782255,"text":"For all or at least most of us, it's not,"},{"time":785823,"text":"probably because it's not \"resisting\"\nin the eyes of the law."},{"time":790550,"text":"In most countries,"},{"time":792044,"text":"the laws still require\nthat the victim prove her innocence --"},{"time":798392,"text":"that's right: the victim needs\nto prove her innocence --"},{"time":802804,"text":"by showing marks on her body"},{"time":805704,"text":"as evidence that she engaged\nin a vigorous and continuous fight"},{"time":810698,"text":"with her aggressor."},{"time":814157,"text":"I can assure you, in most court cases,"},{"time":818502,"text":"no amount of marks is ever enough."},{"time":823633,"text":"I listened to many women's stories."},{"time":828299,"text":"And I didn't hear any of them\ntalking about themselves"},{"time":834406,"text":"as if they had been reduced to a thing,"},{"time":837505,"text":"totally subjected\nto the will of the other."},{"time":842949,"text":"Rather, they sounded astonished\nand even a little proud"},{"time":848912,"text":"looking back"},{"time":851978,"text":"and thinking how clear-headed\nthey had been at the time,"},{"time":856057,"text":"of how much attention\nthey paid to every detail,"},{"time":859247,"text":"as if that would allow them to exert\nsome control over what was happening."}]},{"cues":[{"time":867302,"text":"Then I realized,"},{"time":870086,"text":"of course --"},{"time":871269,"text":"what women are doing in these situations"},{"time":875805,"text":"is negotiating."},{"time":879099,"text":"They're trading sex for life."},{"time":885822,"text":"They ask the aggressor to finish quickly,"},{"time":890506,"text":"so everything is over as soon as possible\nand at the lowest cost."},{"time":896024,"text":"They subject themselves to penetration,"},{"time":901708,"text":"because believe it or not,"},{"time":905176,"text":"penetration is what keeps them furthest"},{"time":909536,"text":"from a sexual or emotional scenario."},{"time":914397,"text":"They subject themselves to penetration,"},{"time":917473,"text":"because penetration is less painful"},{"time":922034,"text":"than kisses, caresses and gentle words."}]},{"cues":[{"time":930541,"text":"Now, if we continue to expect"},{"time":935051,"text":"rape to be what it very rarely is --"},{"time":940599,"text":"with the rapist as a depraved\nlower-class man"},{"time":944682,"text":"and not a university student\nor a businessman"},{"time":948634,"text":"who goes out chasing after girls\non a Friday or Saturday;"},{"time":952607,"text":"if we keep expecting\nthe victims to be demure women"},{"time":957997,"text":"who faint on the scene,"},{"time":961064,"text":"and not self-confident women --"},{"time":965853,"text":"we will continue to be unable to listen."},{"time":970017,"text":"Women will continue to be unable to speak."},{"time":974963,"text":"And we will all continue to be responsible"},{"time":979857,"text":"for that silence"},{"time":982288,"text":"and their solitude."}]},{"cues":[{"time":985433,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}